### Apply Leave (employee)
POST http://localhost:3005/api/leaves/apply
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "Casual",
  "startDate": "2026-03-29",
  "endDate": "2026-03-30",
  "reason": "Personal work"
}

### Get My Leaves
GET http://localhost:3005/api/leaves/my

### Get Leave Balance
GET http://localhost:3005/api/leaves/balance

### Get Pending Leaves (admin/manager)
GET http://localhost:3005/api/leaves/pending

### Approve Leave (admin/manager)
POST http://localhost:3005/api/leaves/LEAVE_ID/approve
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Reject Leave (admin/manager)
POST http://localhost:3005/api/leaves/LEAVE_ID/reject
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Insufficient balance"
}

### Holidays list
GET http://localhost:3005/api/holidays

### Create Holiday (admin)
POST http://localhost:3005/api/holidays
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Holi",
  "date": "2026-03-30",
  "type": "public",
  "description": "Festival of colors"
}

### Employee Detail (admin/manager)
GET http://localhost:3005/api/employees/EMPLOYEE_ID

### Attendance History (admin/manager or employee)
GET http://localhost:3005/api/attendance/history?employeeId=EMPLOYEE_ID&page=1&limit=25

### Attendance History (filtered)
GET http://localhost:3005/api/attendance/history?employeeId=EMPLOYEE_ID&status=Late&start=2026-03-01&end=2026-03-31&page=1&limit=25

### Bulk Shift Assignment (admin)
PATCH http://localhost:3005/api/work-schedule
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userIds": ["EMPLOYEE_ID_1", "EMPLOYEE_ID_2"],
  "shiftType": "FT_MAIN"
}
